winter's police raid, Johnson's bodyguard was shot and killed in an early morning fight while he and Johnson were at a Chicago nightclub. Johnson was suspended by the Bears for one game for being at the club. The 25-year-old Johnson has played in three NFL seasons after attending the University of Washington. Goodell said he would review the matter no later than October 1 to assess Johnson's progress and determine whether the suspension should be reduced. &copy; Reuters 2007. All rights reserved. Late Rodriguez homer lifts Yankees past Red Sox Editors Choice: Best pictures from the last 24 hours. Notes by Napoleon, Churchill found in laundry room Tiananmen Square, 18 years later" /> Tiananmen Square, 18 years later Feeling blue? Study says marriage might cheer you up START News Content Page Tags 'Text' | 'Picture' | 'Slideshow' | 'Video' ie. headline for article ie. headline for article END News Content Page Tags Thousands of revellers take part in one of Bolivia's most important festivals, the Feast of the Lord of Great Power. Iran president sees "countdown" to Israel's end U.S., NATO call Putin missile remarks unhelpful I'm the world's only true democrat, says Putin Iraq Qaeda group says killed captured U.S. troops DUBAI (Reuters) - An al Qaeda-led group in Iraq signaled in a Web video on Monday that it had killed three U.S. soldiers after capturing them last month, showing only pictures of ID cards of two missing U.S. soldiers. Loews bets on natural gas in $4 billion Dominion deal Paris Hilton begins jail term a day early Strikers have new gripe--no sex Apple says iPhone to go on sale June 29 Watch this week's video shows Covering the hottest new gadgets and killer apps All the glitz and glamour of the world of entertainment Reuters Oddly Enough: And Finally&#8230; The quirky, strange but true side of world news Reuters in Second Life Reuters is the world's largest international multimedia news agency, providing investing news, world news, business news, technolo